Functions.html#/s:F10SDGCaching12cachedR.name: cachedResult(cache:computation:)
Functions.html#/s:F10SDGCaching12cachedR.abstract: If cache is non‐nil, its contents are immediately returned; if cache is nil, the result of computation is evaluated, returned, and stored in cache for future calls.

Functions.html#/s:F10SDGCaching12cachedR.name: cachedResult(cache:parameter:computation:)
Functions.html#/s:F10SDGCaching12cachedR.abstract: If cache[parameter] is non‐nil, its contents are immediately returned; if cache[parameter] is nil, the result of computation is evaluated, returned, and stored in cache[parameter] for future calls.
